{"tid":793233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那女童港鐵車廂小便尿流滿地，其父更多次說：「沒事的」、「別煩別煩」。","createTime":"2018-08-25T08:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T18:55:27.000Z","uid":1886,"like":260,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"b9cb4e19ad2819427fed4dd9f6936fe847dd9ee0","tid":793233,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T08:48:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/800191-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%96%91%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%82%E5%B0%8F%E4%BE%BF%E5%B0%BF%E6%B5%81%E6%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0+%E6%AF%8D%E6%80%A5%E6%8A%B9%E5%9C%B0%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F800191-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25BB%2582%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E5%25B0%25BF%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E5%259C%25B0%2B%25E6%25AF%258D%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%258A%25B9%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25AD%2589&d=I7VlNXgm3wFYfUDknKxengdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=951cd89e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F800191-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25BB%2582%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E5%25B0%25BF%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E5%259C%25B0%2B%25E6%25AF%258D%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%258A%25B9%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25AD%2589&h=26320484\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/800191-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%96%91%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%82%E5%B0%8F%E4%BE%BF%E5%B0%BF%E6%B5%81%E6%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0+%E6%AF%8D%E6%80%A5%E6%8A%B9%E5%9C%B0%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89</a><br />\n<br />\n小朋友搭港鐵時尿急，家長會如何做？近日網上流傳一段影片，一對操普通話的父母帶同女兒乘搭港鐵時，竟讓女兒在車廂座位上小便，小便更在車廂地面流開。不少網民鬧爆該對父母行為離譜。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180824/_2018082416350143215.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180824%2F_2018082416350143215.jpg&h=1fee81d1&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n有網民在社交網站facebook群組「PLAY HARD 玩硬」上載影片，由影片可見，在大埔站往太和站的東鐵綫上，有女童在地鐵上公然小便，尿液更沿地面流開，疑似女童母親的女子則不斷用廁紙抹地。乘客見狀出言批評「有冇搞錯，係度痾尿。」該女子則以普通話回應，「不是故意的，不好意思」，乘客說完出面有廁所後便離開座位。女子則一直用手上的卷紙抹地上的尿液，而疑似為父親的男子則一直抱著女童，更多次說「沒事的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」、「別煩別煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。<br />\n<br />\n女子抹了近3分鐘，向女童說「沒關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，而且向別人解釋女童小便是因爲「她憋不住了」。期間有其他乘客提供膠袋給該女子，而女子表示感謝後，將地上一堆抹小便用的紙巾裝進膠袋内。<br />\n<br />\n影片引發網民爭議，不少網民留言批評該對父母行為離譜，「傳播病菌病毒由始起&hellip;無人即時按對講機通知車長？」、「港鐵收佢清潔費啦，有病」、「根本無理過別人感受」、「唔怪得有時會聞到廁所味道，原來係乾咗」，亦有人留言稱「呢啲就喺文化同教育問題」。"},{"pid":"4305296c7ea3cce757ec0c37329f976a46b73dc4","tid":793233,"uid":1247,"like":225,"dislike":4,"score":221,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T08:49:23.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒"},{"pid":"ec2eee71b6fa7d0ebd689a03629a16d63de3d1d5","tid":793233,"uid":122709,"like":8,"dislike":64,"score":-56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T08:51:10.000Z","msg":"父愛的偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a3a40d7799c7b343cba7e2d342dfa03260fc34","tid":793233,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T08:52:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100006915223758/videos/2120768901496930/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100006915223758%2Fvideos%2F2120768901496930%2F&d=I7VlNXgm3wFYfUDknKxengdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNm